query:
SELECT te.id, te.workDate, te.hoursWorked, e.firstName, e.lastName, 
YEAR(te.workDate) as year, MONTH(te.workDate) as month
FROM timeEntries te
JOIN employeeProjectAssignments epa ON te.assignmentId = epa.id
JOIN employees e ON epa.employeeId = e.id
WHERE e.firstName = 'Maciej' AND e.lastName = 'K'
